Conner Oaks 6/27/2023

1. Define advertising and explain where advertising fits in the 4Ps of marketing.

Advertising is the process by which compaines connect with consumers to sell a product, brand, or an idea. As to how the four P's; product, price, place, and promotion; fit in, you need to hit at least one of them, Advertising a product can be used to show off new features, or the highlights of a product. Advertising a price could be showing off a budget product/experience. Advertising a place could be showing off a new location or a new market. Advertising a promotion could be something like the currently upcoming Amazon Prime Day.


